# Quick Reference

Fast lookup for creating new templates from Figma designs.

## File Creation Checklist

```markdown
Given slug: [slug]

- [ ] Create `src/page-[slug].php`
- [ ] Create `src/static/scss/pages/[slug].scss`
- [ ] Create `src/static/js/pages/[slug].bundle.js`
- [ ] Create `src/static/media/images/[slug]/` (for template images)
- [ ] Add '[slug]' to HONE_PAGE_TEMPLATES in `src/functions.php`
- [ ] Run `yarn build` from themes/HoneLandingPages/
- [ ] Test at http://localhost:8081/[wordpress-page-slug]/
```

## Template Header (Copy/Paste)

```php
<?php
// Template Name: [Display Name]

global $class_names, $linkbar_vars;

$template_name = '[slug]';
$class_names[] = $template_name;
$theme_folder = get_bloginfo('stylesheet_directory');
$qs = get_query_string();

$checkout_url = 'https://start.honehealth.com/product/hermes/labtest-hrt-1' . (!empty($qs) ? '?' . $qs : '');

$linkbar_vars = [
    'linkbar_content' => '$45 test + online doctor consultation included. <span class="underline">Start Now</span>',
    'linkbar_link' => $checkout_url,
];

wp_enqueue_script('hone-page-' . $template_name);

get_header();
?>
```

## Template Footer (Copy/Paste)

```php
<?php get_footer(); ?>
```

With Trustpilot:
```php
<script type="text/javascript" src="//widget.trustpilot.com/bootstrap/v5/tp.widget.bootstrap.min.js" async=""></script>
<?php get_footer(); ?>
```

## SCSS File Header (Copy/Paste)

```scss
/**
 * [Display Name]
 * Page-specific styles for page-[slug].php
 */
@use '../variables/colors' as colors;
@use '../variables/fonts' as fonts;
@use '../variables/layout' as layout;

.[slug] {
    // All template styles scoped to template class
}
```

## JS Bundle Header (Copy/Paste)

```javascript
/**
 * [Display Name]
 * Page-specific JavaScript for page-[slug].php
 */
import { initCarousel } from '../utilities/carousel.js';
import '../utilities/accordion.js';
// import { initQuiz } from '../utilities/quiz.js';
// import { initStickyCTA } from '../utilities/stickyCTA.js';

document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
    // Carousel initialization
    // initCarousel({}, '.reviews');
});
```

## Color Quick Reference

| Name | Hex | Use |
|------|-----|-----|
| Black (text) | `colors.$color-black` / `#0E0B20` | Primary text & dark backgrounds |
| Yellow (CTA) | `colors.$color-yellow` / `#F8F93F` | Buttons |
| Yellow hover | `colors.$color-yellow-vital-hover` / `#EDEE39` | Stat highlights |
| Gray light | `colors.$color-gray-light` / `#F1F0EF` | Light section backgrounds |
| Gray medium | `colors.$color-gray-medium` / `#D2CEC4` | Quiz/FAQ backgrounds |
| Gray text | `colors.$color-gray` / `#605B52` | Secondary text |
| White off | `colors.$color-white-off` / `#FCFCFA` | Card backgrounds |
| Green | `colors.$color-green-dark` / `#119555` | Progress bar |

## Font Quick Reference

| Font | Variable | Use |
|------|----------|-----|
| STIX Two Text | `fonts.$STIX-Two-Text` | Headlines, display, prices |
| DM Sans | `fonts.$DM-Sans` | Body, buttons, subheadings |
| Azeret Mono | `fonts.$Azeret-Mono` | Stats, labels, prices |

## Breakpoint Quick Reference

```scss
// Mobile-first (rare in this theme - theme is desktop-first)
// Desktop = default, then override down:

@media #{layout.$medium-screen-and-smaller} {
    // Tablet: ≤ 1024px
}

@media #{layout.$small-screen-and-smaller} {
    // Mobile: ≤ 600px
}
```

## Section Padding Quick Reference

```scss
// Standard section
padding: 80px 64px;                                    // Desktop
@media #{layout.$medium-screen-and-smaller} { padding: 56px 32px; }  // Tablet
@media #{layout.$small-screen-and-smaller} { padding: 40px 15px; }   // Mobile

// Compact section
padding: 64px;                                         // Desktop
@media #{layout.$medium-screen-and-smaller} { padding: 32px; }       // Tablet
@media #{layout.$small-screen-and-smaller} { padding: 24px 15px; }   // Mobile
```

## CTA Button (Copy/Paste)

```scss
.cta-button {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background-color: colors.$color-yellow;
    color: colors.$color-black;
    font-family: fonts.$DM-Sans;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 24px;
    letter-spacing: 0.8px;
    padding: 12px 32px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    border: none;
    text-decoration: none;
    cursor: pointer;

    &:hover {
        background-color: colors.$color-yellow-dark;
    }
}
```

## Figma → SCSS Translation Cheat Sheet

| Figma Tailwind | SCSS Equivalent |
|---------------|-----------------|
| `bg-[#F1F0EF]` | `background-color: colors.$color-gray-light;` |
| `bg-[#0E0B20]` | `background-color: colors.$color-black;` |
| `bg-[#F8F93F]` | `background-color: colors.$color-yellow;` |
| `text-[54px]` | `font-size: 54px;` |
| `font-['STIX_Two_Text']` | `font-family: fonts.$STIX-Two-Text;` |
| `font-['DM_Sans']` | `font-family: fonts.$DM-Sans;` |
| `font-['Azeret_Mono']` | `font-family: fonts.$Azeret-Mono;` |
| `leading-none` | `line-height: 1;` |
| `leading-[1.1]` | `line-height: 1.1;` |
| `leading-[1.4]` | `line-height: 1.4;` |
| `tracking-[-1.08px]` | `letter-spacing: -1.08px;` |
| `gap-[24px]` | `gap: 24px;` |
| `p-[64px]` | `padding: 64px;` |
| `px-[32px] py-[12px]` | `padding: 12px 32px;` |
| `rounded-[2px]` | `border-radius: 2px;` |
| `rounded-[15px]` | `border-radius: 15px;` |
| `flex flex-col` | `display: flex; flex-direction: column;` |
| `flex-[1_0_0]` | `flex: 1;` |
| `items-center` | `align-items: center;` |
| `justify-center` | `justify-content: center;` |
| `shrink-0` | `flex-shrink: 0;` |
| `overflow-clip` | `overflow: hidden;` |
| `self-stretch` | `align-self: stretch;` |

## Carousel HTML Pattern

```html
<!-- Prefix = ".reviews" -->
<div class="reviews-carousel">
    <div class="slide">...</div>
    <div class="slide">...</div>
</div>
<div class="reviews-nav">
    <button class="reviews-prev nav-arrow">&lsaquo;</button>
    <div class="reviews-dots">
        <span class="nav-dot active" data-slide="0"></span>
        <span class="nav-dot" data-slide="1"></span>
    </div>
    <button class="reviews-next nav-arrow">&rsaquo;</button>
</div>
```

```javascript
initCarousel({}, '.reviews');
```

## FAQ HTML Pattern

```html
<div class="faq-item">
    <div class="faq-header" role="button" tabindex="0" aria-expanded="false">
        <span class="faq-question">Question?</span>
        <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-content">
        <div class="faq-item-answer">
            <p>Answer.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
```

```javascript
import '../utilities/accordion.js'; // Auto-initializes
```

## Quiz HTML Pattern

```html
<section class="quiz-section">
    <div class="question-container">
        <div class="progress-bar"></div>
        <h2 id="question"></h2>
        <div id="options" class="options-container"></div>
        <button id="quiz-cta" class="cta-button" style="display:none;">Continue</button>
    </div>
    <div class="results-container" style="display:none;"></div>
</section>
```

```javascript
import { initQuiz } from '../utilities/quiz.js';

const quizData = [
    { id: 1, title: 'Question?', type: 'single-select', options: [
        { id: 0, value: 'Answer 1' },
        { id: 1, value: 'Answer 2' },
    ]},
];

const quizResultContent = [
    { header: 'Result', body: 'Text' },
];

initQuiz({ quizData, quizResultContent, themeFolder: '' });
```

## Build Commands

```bash
cd buy-honehealth-com/themes/HoneLandingPages

yarn install            # First time only
yarn build:assets       # Compile CSS + JS (no copy)
yarn build              # Full build (compile + copy to build/)
yarn watch:assets       # Watch mode for development
```

## Common Mistakes

| Mistake | Fix |
|---------|-----|
| Slug mismatch between files | Check PHP filename, `$template_name`, SCSS filename, JS filename, and `HONE_PAGE_TEMPLATES` array — ALL must match |
| Missing `global $class_names` | Must declare at top of template |
| Styles not loading | Check slug is in `HONE_PAGE_TEMPLATES` array |
| JS not loading | Check `wp_enqueue_script('hone-page-' . $template_name)` is called |
| Fonts not rendering | Don't add @font-face — fonts are in main.css |
| Wrong SCSS import path | Use `@use '../variables/colors'` not `@use 'variables/colors'` |
| Styles leaking to other pages | Wrap all styles in `.[slug] { ... }` |
| Images broken | Use `$theme_folder . '/static/media/images/...'` |
| PHP string syntax error | Escape quotes: `'I\'m'` not `'I'm'` |
| Carousel not working | Check jQuery is loaded, correct prefix naming, import carousel.js |

## PHP String Escaping

```php
// CORRECT
'I\'m able to share...'
'It\'s been over a year...'
'5\'8" and 210 pounds'

// WRONG (will cause syntax error)
'I'm able to share...'
```

## Image Path Pattern

```php
// Template-specific images
$theme_folder . '/static/media/images/' . $template_name . '/hero.webp'

// Shared images (icons, logos)
$theme_folder . '/static/media/images/trustpilot-stars.svg'
$theme_folder . '/static/media/images/icon-shipping.svg'
```

## Tracking Attributes

```php
// All clickable elements
data-trackable="[section]-[element]"
data-interaction="0"

// Examples
data-trackable="hero-cta"
data-trackable="pricing-cta"
data-trackable="how-it-works-cta"
data-trackable="quiz-start"
```

