# Section Library

Reusable section patterns with PHP and SCSS code templates, derived from the Figma reference design.

Each section below includes the PHP structure, SCSS skeleton, and notes on responsive behavior. Use `RESPONSIVE_PATTERNS.md` for detailed breakpoint rules.

---

## 1. Hero Section

Split layout with text content on the left and a full-bleed image on the right.

### PHP

```php
<section class="hero">
    <div class="hero__content">
        <div class="hero__trustpilot">
            <span class="trustpilot-label">Excellent</span>
            <img src="<?php echo $theme_folder; ?>/static/media/images/trustpilot-stars.svg" alt="Trustpilot rating" class="trustpilot-stars" />
            <span class="trustpilot-count">3,966 reviews on</span>
            <img src="<?php echo $theme_folder; ?>/static/media/images/trustpilot-logo.svg" alt="Trustpilot" class="trustpilot-logo" />
        </div>

        <h1 class="hero__title">Get Your Energy, Muscle, and Love Life Back</h1>
        <p class="hero__subtitle">And all the other benefits that come with raising your Testosterone levels safely.</p>

        <div class="hero__cta">
            <a href="<?php echo $checkout_url; ?>" class="cta-button" data-trackable="hero-cta" data-interaction="0">
                Check my levels for $50
            </a>
            <div class="hero__badges">
                <div class="hero__badge">
                    <img src="<?php echo $theme_folder; ?>/static/media/images/icon-shipping.svg" alt="" />
                    <span>Free Shipping</span>
                </div>
                <div class="hero__badge">
                    <img src="<?php echo $theme_folder; ?>/static/media/images/icon-offer.svg" alt="" />
                    <span>Limited Time Discount</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero__image">
        <img src="<?php echo $theme_folder; ?>/static/media/images/<?php echo $template_name; ?>/hero.webp" alt="Hero image" />
    </div>
</section>
```

### SCSS Skeleton

```scss
.hero {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    background-color: colors.$color-gray-light;

    @media #{layout.$medium-screen-and-smaller} {
        flex-direction: column;
    }

    &__content {
        flex: 1;
        padding: 64px;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 32px;

        @media #{layout.$medium-screen-and-smaller} {
            padding: 40px 32px;
        }

        @media #{layout.$small-screen-and-smaller} {
            padding: 22.5px 15px;
            gap: 15px;
        }
    }

    &__trustpilot {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
        font-family: fonts.$DM-Sans;
        font-size: 12px;
        line-height: 16px;
        color: colors.$color-black;
    }

    &__title {
        font-family: fonts.$STIX-Two-Text;
        font-weight: 400;
        font-size: 54px;
        line-height: 1;
        letter-spacing: -1.08px;
        color: colors.$color-black;

        @media #{layout.$medium-screen-and-smaller} {
            font-size: 36px;
            letter-spacing: -0.72px;
        }
    }

    &__subtitle {
        font-family: fonts.$DM-Sans;
        font-weight: 400;
        font-size: 28px;
        line-height: 1.1;
        letter-spacing: -0.56px;
        color: colors.$color-black;

        @media #{layout.$medium-screen-and-smaller} {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 500;
            letter-spacing: -0.36px;
        }
    }

    &__cta {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 16px;
    }

    &__badges {
        display: flex;
        gap: 32px;

        @media #{layout.$medium-screen-and-smaller} {
            gap: 24px;
        }
    }

    &__badge {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
        font-family: fonts.$Azeret-Mono;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.2;

        @media #{layout.$medium-screen-and-smaller} {
            font-size: 12px;
            gap: 4px;

            img { width: 20px; height: 20px; }
        }

        img {
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
        }
    }

    &__image {
        width: 720px;
        flex-shrink: 0;
        align-self: stretch;

        @media #{layout.$medium-screen-and-smaller} {
            width: 100%;
            height: 464px;
            order: -1; // Image on top
        }

        @media #{layout.$small-screen-and-smaller} {
            height: auto;
            aspect-ratio: 360 / 218;
        }

        img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            display: block;
        }
    }
}
```

---

## 2. Social Proof Bar

