# Responsive Design Patterns

How each section type adapts across the three Figma breakpoints and the corresponding SCSS breakpoint approach.

## Breakpoint System

### Figma Frames → SCSS Breakpoints

| Figma Frame | Width | SCSS Breakpoint Variable | Media Query |
|-------------|-------|-------------------------|-------------|
| Desktop | 1440px | Default (no media query) | — |
| Tablet | 768px | `$medium-screen-and-smaller` | `max-width: 1024px` |
| Mobile | 393px | `$small-screen-and-smaller` | `max-width: 600px` |

### Available SCSS Breakpoint Variables

```scss
$xsmall-screen: 375px;
$small-screen: 600px;       // Mobile breakpoint
$medium-screen: 1024px;     // Tablet breakpoint
$large-screen: 1280px;
$xlarge-screen: 1440px;     // Desktop design width
```

### Standard Media Query Pattern

```scss
.element {
    // Desktop styles (default)
    padding: 64px;
    font-size: 54px;

    @media #{$medium-screen-and-smaller} {
        // Tablet adjustments
        padding: 32px;
        font-size: 36px;
    }

    @media #{$small-screen-and-smaller} {
        // Mobile adjustments
        padding: 15px;
        font-size: 28px;
    }
}
```

## Section-by-Section Responsive Behavior

### Hero Section

| Property | Desktop (1440px) | Tablet (768px) | Mobile (393px) |
|----------|-----------------|----------------|----------------|
| Layout | Horizontal (text + image side-by-side) | Vertical (image top, text bottom) | Vertical (image top, text bottom) |
| Image | Right half, 720px wide, full height | Full width, ~464px tall | Full width, aspect-ratio preserved |
| Content padding | 64px | 32px horizontal, 40px vertical | 15px horizontal, 22.5px vertical |
| Title font | 54px STIX Two Text | 36px STIX Two Text | 36px STIX Two Text |
| Subtitle font | 28px DM Sans | 18px DM Sans Medium | 18px DM Sans Medium |
| CTA badge text | 16px Azeret Mono | 12px Azeret Mono | 12px Azeret Mono |
| Badge icons | 24px | 20px | 20px |
| Badge gap | 32px between items | 24px between items | 24px between items |

```scss
.hero {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    background-color: $color-gray-light;

    @media #{$medium-screen-and-smaller} {
        flex-direction: column;
    }

    &__content {
        flex: 1;
        padding: 64px;

        @media #{$medium-screen-and-smaller} {
            padding: 40px 32px;
            order: 2; // Text below image
        }

        @media #{$small-screen-and-smaller} {
            padding: 22.5px 15px;
        }
    }

    &__image {
        width: 720px;
        align-self: stretch;

        @media #{$medium-screen-and-smaller} {
            width: 100%;
            height: 464px;
            order: 1; // Image on top
        }

        @media #{$small-screen-and-smaller} {
            height: auto;
            aspect-ratio: 360 / 218;
        }

        img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
        }
    }
}
```

### Social Proof / Title Bar

| Property | Desktop | Tablet | Mobile |
|----------|---------|--------|--------|
| Layout | 4 cards in a row | 2×2 grid or horizontal scroll | Horizontal scroll carousel |
| Card padding | 16px | 16px | 16px |
| Section padding | 56px 64px | 40px 32px | 32px 15px |
| Heading font | 28px | 28px | 22px |
| Navigation | None | None | Dot indicators shown |

### Quiz Question

| Property | Desktop | Tablet | Mobile |
|----------|---------|--------|--------|
| Question width | 632px centered | Full width minus padding | Full width minus padding |
| Question font | 40px STIX Two Text | 36px | 28px |
| Answer layout | 2×2 grid (312px wide each, 18px gap) | 2×2 grid (smaller widths) | Stacked single column |
| Answer button height | 64px | 56px | 48px |
| Section padding | 48px top, 64px bottom | 32px | 24px 15px |

```scss
.quiz-question {
    .answers {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 312px);
        gap: 18px;
        justify-content: center;

        @media #{$medium-screen-and-smaller} {
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        }

        @media #{$small-screen-and-smaller} {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
    }
}
```

### Stats Cards (Why TRT Now)

| Property | Desktop | Tablet | Mobile |
|----------|---------|--------|--------|
| Layout | 4 cards in a row | 2×2 grid | 2×2 grid or horizontal scroll |
| Card width | 25% (flex: 1) | 50% | 50% |
| Stat number font | 60px Azeret Mono | 48px | 36px |
| Section title | 54px centered | 36px | 28px |
| Section padding | 80px 64px | 56px 32px | 40px 15px |

### Testimonial Carousel (Dark Section)

| Property | Desktop | Tablet | Mobile |
|----------|---------|--------|--------|
| Layout | Text left (50%) + Card right (416px) | Text top + Card bottom (full width) | Stacked, full width |
| Title font | 54px | 36px | 28px |
| Card width | 416px | Full width | Full width |
| Review image | 352×198 | Full width × proportional | Full width × proportional |
| Navigation | Arrows + dots below card | Arrows + dots | Dots only |

### Listicle Section

| Property | Desktop | Tablet | Mobile |
|----------|---------|--------|--------|
| Layout | Alternating image/text side-by-side | Stacked (image top, text bottom) | Stacked |
| Image width | 688px (48%) | Full width | Full width |
| Image height | 416px | 300px | 240px |
| Text padding | 128px horizontal | 48px | 24px |
| Text width | 52% | 100% | 100% |
| Alternation | Odd: text-left/image-right, Even: image-left/text-right | Always image-top/text-bottom | Always image-top/text-bottom |

```scss
.listicle-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;

    @media #{$medium-screen-and-smaller} {
        flex-direction: column;
    }

    &:nth-child(even) {
        flex-direction: row-reverse;

        @media #{$medium-screen-and-smaller} {
            flex-direction: column; // Override reverse on mobile
        }
    }

    &__image {
        width: 688px;
        height: 416px;
        flex-shrink: 0;

        @media #{$medium-screen-and-smaller} {
            width: 100%;
            height: 300px;
        }

        @media #{$small-screen-and-smaller} {
            height: 240px;
        }
    }

    &__text {
        flex: 1;
        padding: 0 128px;

        @media #{$medium-screen-and-smaller} {
            padding: 32px 48px;
        }

        @media #{$small-screen-and-smaller} {
            padding: 24px;
        }
    }
}
```

### What's Included (Product Section)

| Property | Desktop | Tablet | Mobile |
|----------|---------|--------|--------|
| Layout | Image left (50%) + Content right (576px) | Stacked | Stacked |
| Product image | Full height, auto width | Full width, aspect-ratio | Full width |
| Line items | Horizontal with image thumbnails | Same | Stacked, smaller thumbnails |
| Content gap | 80px between image and content | 40px | 24px |

### How It Works (Steps Cards)

| Property | Desktop | Tablet | Mobile |
|----------|---------|--------|--------|
| Layout | 3 cards in a row | 3 cards in a row (smaller) | Stacked or horizontal scroll |
| Card width | 33% | 33% | Full width |
| Image height | ~260px | ~200px | ~200px |
| Step badge | 56px circle, yellow, top-left 16px | Same | Same |

### Before/After Reviews (Dark Section)

| Property | Desktop | Tablet | Mobile |
|----------|---------|--------|--------|
| Visible cards | 3-5 in horizontal carousel | 2 | 1 |
| Card width | 360px (image width) | ~340px | Full width |
| Navigation | Arrows + dots | Arrows + dots | Swipe + dots |
| Card layout | Vertical (image → name → quote → body) | Same | Same |

### FAQ Section

| Property | Desktop | Tablet | Mobile |
|----------|---------|--------|--------|
| Content width | 980px centered | Full width minus padding | Full width minus padding |
| Title font | 54px | 36px | 28px |
| Question font | 22px DM Sans Medium | 18px | 16px |
| Section background | `$color-gray-medium` | Same | Same |
| Accordion border | `rgba(96,91,82,0.8)` top+bottom on first, bottom only on rest | Same | Same |

## General Responsive Rules

### Font Size Scaling

| Desktop | Tablet | Mobile |
|---------|--------|--------|
| 54px | 36px | 28px |
| 40px | 36px | 28px |
| 28px | 22px | 18px |
| 22px | 18px | 16px |
| 16px | 16px | 14px |
| 12px | 12px | 12px |

### Padding Scaling

| Desktop | Tablet | Mobile |
|---------|--------|--------|
| 128px | 48px | 24px |
| 80px | 56px | 40px |
| 64px | 32px | 15px |
| 32px | 24px | 15px |
| 16px | 16px | 12px |

### Layout Pattern

Desktop → Tablet → Mobile:
- **Horizontal → Stacked**: Most 2-column layouts stack at tablet
- **4-col → 2-col → 1-col**: Card grids progressively reduce columns
- **Carousel visible**: Desktop shows most, mobile shows 1
- **Side margins**: 64px → 32px → 15px

# Design System: Figma Tokens → SCSS Variables

Complete mapping between Figma design tokens and the theme's SCSS variables/conventions.

## Colors

### Figma Token → SCSS Variable

| Figma Token Name | Hex Value | SCSS Variable | Usage |
|-----------------|-----------|---------------|-------|
| Blue Gray Night/100% | `#0E0B20` | `$color-black` | Primary text, dark backgrounds |
| White | `#FCFCFA` | `$color-white-off` | Card backgrounds, light text on dark |
| White (pure) | `#FFFFFF` | `$color-white` | Pure white backgrounds |
| Gray Light | `#F1F0EF` | `$color-gray-light` | Light section backgrounds, hero bg |
| Gray Mid/100% | `#D2CEC4` | `$color-gray-medium` | Quiz bg, FAQ bg, muted elements |
| Gray Dark/100% | `#605B52` | `$color-gray` | Secondary text, metadata |
| Gray Dark/80% | `rgba(96,91,82,0.8)` | `$color-black-lightest` | Tertiary text, borders |
| Vital Yellow/100% | `#F8F93F` | `$color-yellow` | Primary CTA buttons |
| Vital Yellow/Hover | `#EDEE39` | `$color-yellow-vital-hover` | Stat highlight backgrounds |
| Green - In Range | `#119555` | `$color-green-dark` | Progress bar active segments |

### Direct Hex Usage (when no variable exists)

Some colors appear in Figma that are used directly:
- `#D4CDC2` — Hero image placeholder background (use inline)
- `#20C475` — Verified badge green (use inline)
- `rgba(96,91,82,0.8)` — FAQ borders, tertiary text (use `$color-black-lightest`)

## Typography

### Font Families

| Figma Font | SCSS Variable | CSS Value | Usage |
|-----------|---------------|-----------|-------|
| STIX Two Text | `$STIX-Two-Text` | `"STIX Two Text", serif` | Headlines, display text, prices |
| STIX Two Math | `$STIX-Two-Text` | `"STIX Two Text", serif` | Same font family — Figma calls it "Math" variant |
| DM Sans | `$DM-Sans` | `"DM Sans", sans-serif` | Body text, buttons, labels, subheadings |
| Azeret Mono | `$Azeret-Mono` | `"Azeret Mono", monospace` | Stats/numbers, labels, prices |

**Important:** Figma references "STIX Two Math" — use the same `$STIX-Two-Text` variable. They're the same font family.

### Typography Scale

| Figma Token | Font | Size | Weight | Line-Height | Letter-Spacing | SCSS Approach |
|------------|------|------|--------|-------------|----------------|---------------|
| Display/XL | STIX Two Text | 54px | 400 | 1 (54px) | -1.08px (-2%) | Desktop headlines |
| Display/L | STIX Two Text | 36px | 400 | 1 (36px) | -0.72px (-2%) | Tablet/mobile headlines |
| Display/D3 | STIX Two Text | 40px | 400 | 48px | 0 | Quiz questions, section titles |
| Display/D5 | STIX Two Text | 24px | 400 | 32px | 0 | List item prices, section subtitles |
| Display/S | STIX Two Text | 20px | 400 | 0.96 | -1% | Small display text |
| Heading/XL | DM Sans | 28px | 400 | 1.1 | -0.56px (-2%) | Subheadings |
| Heading/L | DM Sans | 22px | 500 | 1.1 | -0.44px (-2%) | Card headings, stat descriptions |
