## 12. Tout + Review Carousel (Care Callout)

Split tout (title + featured quote + CTA left, photo grid right) above a Slick review cards carousel. See opt-longevity `.care-callout` for the full implementation. Key notes:

- Doctor/testimonial photo grid: 2×2 desktop (244:282 aspect ratio, 20px radius), 4-in-a-row strip mobile
- Carousel: `infinite: true` + `centerMode: true`, 3 cards desktop / 1 mobile with 40px peek
- **Requires** the `[aria-hidden="true"]` SCSS override (see QUICK_REFERENCE) because `infinite: true` creates clones
- Nav dots use `appendDots` → must style `.slick-dots` (not `.nav-dot`) — see QUICK_REFERENCE carousel pattern

